      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DAPPER CHAP (1) is progressing well scoring last time out (24.99) at this track and bringing up his 12th career win. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Has put together a string of wins and expected to go close again. WHODAT JEWEL (2) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey here having won three of five starts. Scored by a neck last time (23.95) in a Grade 5 over 425m at Traralgon. Among the main chances. ELECTROJET (8) finished in the minors last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 425m at Bendigo, taking a Group Listed in an exceptional 23.78. Should be in this for a long way. MATCHBOX BEAST (3) was out of placings last time (23.95) at Bendigo in a Grade 4/5, finishing fourth and beaten 7 lengths. Has an unbeaten record from this draw, scoring two times.",
